User Manual:

Mouse/Key combination:

Key ‘b’ - for drawing the bounding box.

Key ‘c’ - for clearing the bounding box.

Key ‘p’ - for switching to perspective projection.

Key ‘o’ - for switching to orthographic projection.

Key ‘w’ - for Moving forward.

Key ’s’ - for moving backward.

Key ‘a’ - for moving left.

Key ‘d’ - for moving right.



